@startuml
title Main Sequence

actor User
participant Application
participant GmailClient
participant AttachmentManager
participant ImageSorter
participant HtmlGenerator
participant WordPressClient
participant HistoryManager

User -> Application: execute
Application -> GmailClient: fetch unread mails
GmailClient --> Application: mails
Application -> AttachmentManager: save attachments
AttachmentManager --> Application: image paths
Application -> ImageSorter: sort images
ImageSorter --> Application: sorted images
Application -> HtmlGenerator: generate HTML
HtmlGenerator --> Application: content
Application -> WordPressClient: upload media
WordPressClient --> Application: media ids
Application -> WordPressClient: create post
WordPressClient --> Application: post id / url
Application -> HistoryManager: save history

@enduml
